high_descs: turn right to face the wood table
pick up the knife behind the tomato on the table
face the tomato on the wood table
slice half of the tomato
turn right to face the kitchen sink
place the knife on the left front edge of the sink
return to the wood table and look at the sliced tomato
pick up a slice of tomato on the wood table
go to the right of the table and face the microwave
place the tomato in the microwave and heat it for several seconds before removing it
face the sink next to the microwave on the counter
place the tomato on the counter in front of the sink, to the right of the knife
anns.task_desc: slice a tomato and place a warmed up slice near the sink

high_descs: Go forward, turn to the right to face the table where the tomato and fork are.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is behind the tomato on the table.
Back up from the table.
Cut the tomato into slices.
Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Put the knife into the sink.
Turn around, go to the sliced tomato on the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn around, go to the left to the sink, turn to the microwave on the left.
Put the tomato in the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the tomato when it is done cooking.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the knife from behind the tomato
Look down at the tomato.
Cut the tomato on the table.
Turn right and head to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around, go back to the sink and turn left toward the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Go back to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the sink.
